  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Slice the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into discs</p><p>Add the <strong>potato discs</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and sprinkle them with<strong> cold water </strong>(this will help the potatoes cook through!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1580294463794-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1580294463794-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1580294463794-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1580294463794-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1580294463794-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, peel and finely dice the <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the<strong> smoked streaky bacon </strong>roughly</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580294487892-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580294487892-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580294487892-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580294487892-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1580294487892-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped bacon </strong>and <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 4-5 min, stirring occasionally, until golden and crisp</p><p>Once the bacon is crisp, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to the pan and cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant</p><p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1580294492187-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1580294492187-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1580294492187-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1580294492187-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1580294492187-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give it all a good mix up</p><p>Gradually add 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span><strong>milk</strong>, a little at a time, and stir everything together until the sauce begins to thicken slightly</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580294498801-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580294498801-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580294498801-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580294498801-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1580294498801-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir through the <strong>double cream</strong> and most of the<strong> grated cheese </strong>(save some for later!)<strong> </strong>and give it all a good mix up<strong> </strong>until the cheese has melted</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>cheesy bacon sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580294502834-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580294502834-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580294502834-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580294502834-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580294502834-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>potato discs</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> in a single layer</p><p>Pour over <strong>half</strong> the <strong>cheesy bacon sauce</strong></p><p>Repeat this process until you have a final layer of<strong> </strong>sauce and top with any leftover <strong>potato discs</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> reserved grated cheese</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>Alpine</strong> <strong>cheesy bacon & potato gratin</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
